Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the deployment and architecture of ultra-dense cellular networks, which involves networking and communication technologies. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of massive MIMO antennas and millimeter wave communication technologies, which are related to information theory. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper may involve multimedia applications and services that can be supported by ultra-dense cellular networks. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the hardware architecture of the ultra-dense cellular network, such as the design of the massive MIMO antennas. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper may involve the control and management of the ultra-dense cellular network, such as the optimization of backhaul network capacity and energy efficiency.
